headline.print_headline: Canizares Fires 69 for 6-Shot Lead in Morocco
headline.main: Canizares Fires 69 for 6-Shot Lead in Morocco

lead_paragraph: Alejandro Canizares of Spain extended his lead to six strokes in the third round of the Trophee Hassan II after shooting a 3-under 69 on Saturday.
